 
----------------------------------------------------------
Source tree

   src         ultravisor source
   include     ultravisor includes
   tools       has build tools,etc
   sim         simics simulator scripts, images for u-boot/Linux
   sg          simple guest -- a simple guest for testing

----------------------------------------------------------
Building and Running

To build/run simple guest on the bare metal

   cd sg
   make
   [path-to-simics]/simics sim/sg.simics
   
   (will print out message on console1)


To build/run Ultravisor with simple guest

   make
   [path-to-simics]/simics sim/uv-sg.simics


----------------------------------------------------------
Current memory layout

   Ultravisor at 0x20000000 phys, 0x20000000 virtual -- in GS=0 address space

   Guest at 0x30000000 phys, 0x00000000 virtual, and 0x00000000 guest-physical  -- in GS=1 address space

----------------------------------------------------------
TLB/MMU

   Current Simics has 16 TLB entries
   Ultravisor take 1 TLB for itself (#15), 1 for CCSR space (#14)

----------------------------------------------------------
